b_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/2ca069dfbf8915938469e60ca95af031.webp?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 Simple Controls: Asterism uses simple and intuitive controls making it easy to pick up and difficult to put down. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀Album Length Experience: Asterism is designed to be played in a single sitting, with approximately 2 hours of gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/b6a64ca0fd9707974977fc857be36a36.avif?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo developer, Claire Morwood, has meticulously crafted nearly every aspect of Asterism, from folding origami avatars & moulding clay lighthouses to writing & voicing the soundtrack. A culmination of years of exploration and experimentation, Asterism is a labour of love and passion that sits at the intersection of music, art, and digital storytelling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/a1d482f0c2c414f5b66c9c8cd4654c35.avif?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/615a01492fef01563c649b9b2176687c.webp?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Asterism was inspired by the feeling of sitting on the window seat of a bus, music echoing in your ears, as you glimpse momentary details amidst the blur of passing lights.”</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claire is a self-taught game designer, artist, programmer, & co-creator of the BAFTA-nominated game <i>Before I Forget</i> (3-Fold Games). She is passionate about empowering others through workshops on game development, particularly in creating personal games using small tools like Bitsy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/31e3ab0445433de758939b015844a073.poster.avif?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/31e3ab0445433de758939b015844a073.webm?t=1738243097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/31e3ab0445433de758939b015844a073.mp4?t=1738243097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/4784fc81641482e687396f07b3fdbaf1.webp?t=1738243097\" width=600 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asterism is supported by Creative Scotland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras/162b4c505a0409e181fe31267b5b5426.avif?t=1738243097\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187450/extras_big/162b4c505a0409e181fe31267b5b5426.avif?t=1738243097 width=800 height=228 /></span></p>",
